import React from 'react';
import { Timeline, Text } from '@mantine/core';

function TimelineComponent() {
    return (
        <ParentTimeline>
            <Timeline bulletSize={24} lineWidth={2}>
                <Timeline.Item color="lime" title="Mathematical Olympiad Workshop Lecturer">
                    <Text color="dimmed" size="sm">Weekly workshops in PREU High School.</Text>
                    <Text size="xs" mt={4}>2019</Text>
                </Timeline.Item>

                <Timeline.Item title="Mathematical Olympiad Seminarist">
                    <Text color="dimmed" size="sm"> Mathematical Olimpiad Workshops in <Text variant="link" component="span" inherit href="https://fi.ort.edu.uy/78235/33">Universidad ORT</Text> and Universidad de Montevideo.</Text>
                    <Text size="xs" mt={4}>2019 - 2020</Text>
                </Timeline.Item>

                <Timeline.Item title="Adjunct Proffesor">
                    <Text color="dimmed" size="sm">Adjunct proffesor in the course of Discrete Mathematics in Universidad ORT.</Text>
                    <Text size="xs" mt={4}>2020</Text>
                </Timeline.Item>

                <Timeline.Item title="Software Engineer">
                    <Text color="dimmed" size="sm">Started as a Junior Software Engineer Intern and then worked as a Software Engineer I in TangoCode Inc.</Text>
                    <Text color="dimmed" size="sm">I worked in agile software projects and web development related to Digital Marketing in the product Chassis.</Text>
                    <Text size="xs" mt={4}>2020 - 2022</Text>
                </Timeline.Item>
            </Timeline>
        </ParentTimeline>
    );
}

export default TimelineComponent;
